          <source>Users will be able to watch clips directly in the game or through your website.</source>
        </trans-unit><trans-unit id="106" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>You plan to log every upload and viewing for use in analytics and for traceability.</source>
        </trans-unit><trans-unit id="107" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>You need a storage solution that can handle thousands of simultaneous uploads, massive amounts of video data, and constantly growing log files.</source>
